en.title: FE's Golf Long Drive Challenge, Penang 18th October 2008.
en.content:
The first Qualifying Event of FE’s Long Drive Challenge at the Penang Golf Resort on 18th October 2008 was a GREAT SUCCESSS!

If you missed out having a go, don’t miss the other Qualifying Events, JB (22nd October 2008, Palm Resort Golf and Country Club) and Kuala Lumpur (29th October 2008, Kelab Golf Sultan Abdul Aziz Shah and 4th November 2008, Saujana Golf and Country Club) with  the Grand Finals on the 05th November 2008 at Saujana Golf and Country Club.

The Golf Fair was well supported with an estimated 1000 people coming through the gates. The exhibitors had all the latest golf equipment on display and many customers walked away with great bargains!
